                          <DESC>
                            <L-2 L="EN">Qualification period of the peripheral signals. NOTE: Qualification period can be set for the pair of 8 GPIOs          For Instance:          Qualification sampling period for GPIO0 to GPIO7:           0x00,QUALPRDx = PLLSYSCLK           0x01,QUALPRDx = PLLSYSCLK/2          0x02,QUALPRDx = PLLSYSCLK/4          ....          0xFF,QUALPRDx = PLLSYSCLK/510          Reset type: SYSRSn</L-2>
                          </DESC>
